request.description:
1. Connect to ws://localhost:8000/ws/chat
2. Receive {type:'hello', conversation_id:'...'}
3. Send Turn 1:
   {"type":"chat","conversation_id":"demo-1","city":"istanbul","message":"I am visiting Istanbul for 5 days and I love history and culture."}
4. Receive streamed {type:'token'} frames then {type:'final'}
5. Send Turn 2 (same connection):
   {"type":"chat","conversation_id":"demo-1","message":"I am vegetarian — which sites have good vegetarian food nearby?"}
   The model will remember turn 1 context.
6. Send Turn 3:
   {"type":"chat","conversation_id":"demo-1","message":"What should I pack for this trip?"}
